%N A015599 Inverse of 1590th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015599 Periodic with period length 1590. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015599 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015599/b015599.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015599 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1590.
%H A015599 <a href="/index/Rec#order_416">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 416.
%H A015599 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015599 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015599 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1590,x],{x,0,130}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Jun 27 2017 *)
%o A015599 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1590)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
%K A015599 sign,easy
%O A015599 0,1
%A A015599 _Simon Plouffe_
